These are Puzzles for 5x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-8-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, juice, lemonade, soy-milk
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: azalea, tulip, aconite, poppy
City: venice, liverpool, hannover, boston
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: western, time-travel, superhero, crime
4 different games are played: snooker, chess, bridge, whist
 1. the person watching superhero movies is on the left or right of the person playing whist##3
 2. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere to the left of the person who growspoppy##5
 3. the person who growstulip is on the far left##1
 4. the person who growsazalea is the person watching time-travel movies##1
 5. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person who growsazalea##1
 6. the person watching time-travel movies is not to the left of the person playing chess##8
 7. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1
 8. the person watching superhero movies is not to the left of the person playing snooker##8
 9. the person playing whist is the person drinking almond-milk##1
10. the person drinking soy-milk is somewhere to the left of the person drinking juice##5
11. the person drinking juice is in an even position##4
12. the person playing bridge is on the left or right of the person playing snooker##3
13. the person traveling to boston is not to the right of the person drinking lemonade##8
14. the person playing bridge is somewhere to the left of the person playing whist##5
15. the person watching time-travel movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching superhero movies##5
16. the person traveling to hannover is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |     2     |      3       |      4      |
| Beverage    | soy-milk | juice     | lemonade     | almond-milk |
| Flower        | tulip  | azalea | aconite      | poppy      |
| City         | boston  | liverpool    | hannover | venice       |
| Movie-Genre       | western | time-travel   | superhero      | crime  |
| Game   | chess      | snooker  | bridge   | whist      |

