The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: rose, orchid, balloon-flower, lily
4 different pets are kept: fish, guinea-pig, pony, rabbit
 1. the person traveling to paris is on the left or right of the person driving the roller##3
 2. the person driving the helicopter is on the left or right of the owner of the guinea-pig##3
 3. the person eating apricot is not to the left of the person who growsorchid##8
 4. the person eating pear is between the person eating apple and the person eating onion##2
 5. the person eating pear is not the owner of the pony##6
 6. the person traveling to prague is somewhere to the left of the person eating apricot##5
 7. the person traveling to paris is not to the right of the owner of the fish##8
 8. the person who growsrose is somewhere to the left of the person eating apricot##5
 9. the person eating pear is somewhere to the right of the person who growsrose##5
10. the person traveling to rome is in an odd position##4
11. the person who growsorchid is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
12. the owner of the pony is not to the right of the owner of the fish##8
13. the person who growsballoon-flower is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to paris##5
14. the person traveling to nizza is the person driving the taxi##1
15. the person traveling to paris is not to the left of the person who growslily##8
16. the owner of the fish is not to the left of the person traveling to paris##8
17. the person traveling to rome is the person driving the helicopter##1
18. the person driving the helicopter is not the person eating apple##6
19. the person driving the snowmobile is not the person traveling to prague##6
20. the person driving the taxi is somewhere to the right of the person eating pear##5
21. the person eating apple is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to nizza##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |      3      |       4        |
