 8. the person eating carrot is not to the left of the person watching drama movies##8
 9. the person eating radish is not to the right of the person watching musical movies##8
10. the person watching drama movies is on the left or right of the person eating eggplant##3
11. the tower house is not to the left of the wooden house##8
12. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person eating eggplant##1
13. the fonseca-smoker is not to the right of the person eating garlic##8
14. the game-smoker is not to the left of the person eating radish##8
15. the townhouse house is on the right of the person eating carrot##1
16. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left or right of the cain-smoker##3
17. the person eating radish is on the left or right of the person watching disaster movies##3
18. the fonseca-smoker is somewhere between the person who's hobby is photography and the person who's hobby is collecting##7
